Lemmings 2 Hard Drive Install Instructions
------------------------------------------

IMPORTANT: To run Lemmings 2 from Hard Drive you need an Amiga with
1 MByte of CHIP RAM plus at least 512K of further RAM. 


To install Lemmings 2 on your hard drive follow these simple steps:


1) Copy all 3 Lemmings II disks into a directory on your hard drive.

2) Copy the contents of this disk into the same directory.

3) Change to this directory, from the CLI type 'HDLemmings2',
   or from workbench double click the  HDL2 icon.

Please note that the version of IconX supplied is for AmigaDOS 2.0.

If you wish to retain your saved game, copy the L2-saved-positions file
from your saved-game floppy into this directory.
 
